snippet: Chris Carter homered twice and drove in three runs, Collin McHugh pitched into the eighth inning and the Houston Astros beat the Los Angeles Angels 4-1 on Wednesday night....

headline.print_headline: Carter's 2 Homers Lead Astros Over Angels 4-1
headline.main: Carter's 2 Homers Lead Astros Over Angels 4-1
